summary: "phantom pains for injuries I’ve never gotten?? And I know it’s probably just an anxiety thing but sometimes I worry it’s like....
question: "phantom pains for injuries I’ve never gotten?? And I know it’s probably just an anxiety thing but sometimes I worry it’s like. premonitions or something? lol"  You mean, phantom pains like Tony Stark keeps getting in his arm, for no apparent reason?  That may be a premonition of a far more terrible pain in his future?  Those kinds of pains?
answer: I mean….the thing with Tony’s arm is *clearly* supposed to be foreshadowing for the viewers but like….he’s injured his body in extreme ways, multiple times before. I’m not convinced the arm pain is supposed to be Premonition instead of just like, long-lasting effects of damage lol.

summary: The Avengers On Halloween Would Include...
title: The Avengers On Halloween Would Include...
body:
you’d be lying if you say the avengers don’t have a huge halloween party together i don’t make the rules

  • they have the ULTIMATE pumpkin carving contest
  • teams of 2
  • bruce is the judge
  • shuri and peter win
  • nobody explained to thor what pumpkin carving was so he just stabbed his and left the knife in it
  • they all dress up as batman unironically
  • except clint dresses as superman
  • “what fuck guys i didn’t get the memo–”
  • they are DIVIDED over candy corn
  • candy corn: civil war
  • tony buys out an entire halloween store’s candy stock
  • so many scary movies
  • shuri, nebula, hope, and gamora don’t bat an eye but the others are pissing themselves
  • literally all of them
  • tony makes robotic bats that fly around the compound at random time intervals
  • he also makes a spider drone army for his son peter so he can be similar to scott lang since he felt left out when he saw the Ants™
  • peter will give candy out in his spiderman suit
  • “are you the real spiderman?”
  • “maybe… but shh, you can’t tell anyone ;)”
  • loki terrorizes kids
  • “i quite like this midgardian holiday!”
  • bucky and steve walk around and reminisce over their childhood halloween memories
  • doctor strange probably starts a random fire somewhere idk
  •  t’challa runs around as black panther in some of the neighborhoods with minorities to make sure nothing bad happens
  • midnight karaoke party
  • tony drunkenly sings a duet of “Tomorrow” from Annie with thor
  • everyone with a device is filming it
  • they also play Just Dance 2
  • all of them are hungover the next morning with the exception of peter, shuri, t’challa, and groot
  • how does a raccoon get drunk, you ask?
  • i have no idea
  • natasha bakes the pillsbury doughboy halloween cookies at like 2AM with wanda
  • vision is just ???
  • cruising down the streets or something idk he’s weird
  • bruce can’t hand out candy because whenever he sees a kid with a hulk costume he Flips
  • “do you KNOW what i have to go through–”
  • drax eats all the candy by himself
  • mantis stares

SPOOKY SCARY SKELETONS

HAPPY HALLOWEEN EVERYBODY!!  I hope you have a good night, and I hope you enjoyed these headcanons!
